    <section class="" data-id="85798" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
     <section class="" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section class="" data-width="100%" style="padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(60, 40, 34); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 670px; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
       <section style="padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px dashed rgb(60, 40, 34); color: inherit; border-radius: 4px; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
        <section style="margin: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
         <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: center; color: rgb(60, 40, 34); border-color: rgb(60, 40, 34); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(99, 36, 35); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong class="" data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">香港电影中的大反派</strong></span></p>
        </section>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
    <p></p>
    <section class="" data-id="85354" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
     <section style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(0, 234, 172); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
       <p style="padding: 0.8em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; border-radius: 0px 0em 0em 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(98, 238, 201); text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(0, 234, 172);"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">上个世纪80年代到90年代中期，是香港电影的黄金时期，这期间无数关于情义，关乎正义的香港电影，上演着一幕幕英雄好汉的故事。在这些电影中，似乎永远都是主角历经艰辛，终于战胜邪恶，还世界公平和正义。</span></p>
       <p style="padding: 0.8em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; border-radius: 0px 0em 0em 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(98, 238, 201); text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(0, 234, 172);"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">俗话说，红花还需绿叶配，烘托主角光环的，正是那些无恶不作的反派角色。若是没有了坏人，好人又有何用呢？正因为有了这些反派角色，电影中的世界会陷入黑暗和不公中，而正是有了这些反派角色，我们正义的主角便有了存在的意义。今天，小编与你一起回顾香港电影中，那些经典的反派演员。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
      </section>
      <section style="margin-top: -18px; margin-right: 8px; margin-left: 8px; max-width: 100%; border-right-width: 90px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(0, 234, 172); border-left-color: rgb(0, 234, 172); display: inline-block; height: 60px; width: 50px; vertical-align: top; float: right; transform: rotate(-50deg); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom-width: 60px !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;"></section>
     </section>
     <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <section class="" data-id="48610" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
     <section style="margin: 30px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 1);">
      <section style="margin-top: -50px; margin-left: -12px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 25px; height: 130px; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); transform: rotate(45deg); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"></section>
      <section class="" data-style="text-align: center;color:rgb(255,255,255);" style="margin: -40px 5px -80px; padding: 5px 5px 30px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 14px;">
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: inherit; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">四大恶人</span></p>
      </section>
      <section style="margin-right: -12px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 25px; height: 130px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); transform: rotate(45deg); float: right; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"></section>
     </section>
     <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.6369747899159663" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYu1vFMCGckqXRcbOA8zohxElHOU0vKKqtibp0mVyuODMdRibOOaQsfAeQ%2F0%3F" data-w="595" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">提到香港电影的反派演员，就不得不提到老牌的四大恶人。他们是：何家驹，成奎安，黄光亮，李兆基。在那个时代的香港电影，呈现出流水线制作的趋势，个人风格一旦定型，就很难脱离，配角一直是配角，反派也一直是反派。出演坏人角色，反而能够深入民心，也自然不是一件容易的事情。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.56" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYFkCd6Vl6OvD3Y8nUSQ59bIu0jicZelQd03Bvwm9YH3ftfiaUrJFY1Zicg%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">单说起这四个人的个人代表作，多半都是和其余三人中的一位共同合作的，四个人几乎承包了一段时期香港电影的反派角色。首先四大恶人之首的何家驹，代表作品包括与刘德华合作的《狱中龙》，李修贤周星驰合作的《霹雳先锋》，以及后来的《古惑仔》系列，每一部不是大哥就是打手。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5575" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vY8qyudZ9dzicMwIbjhG0ClJ56I8oESicEzgviaGrDOBQdBPqB0KphdJp1g%2F0%3F" data-w="400" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">黄光亮的长相很特别，即使观众记不得他的名字，也会对他标志性的大鼻子印象深刻，当然他这个大鼻子也遗传给了他的“儿子”，目前正当红的演员王祖蓝。（此处为调侃，请勿当真）。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">虽然他的长相没有成奎安凶恶，但不妨碍他也是反派角色。代表作品有《霹雳先锋》，《学校风云》，《龙虎风云》。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5416666666666666" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYmNqXKOv0YiaZ5POiaJyvad4K3ONf7gNNHOubr5vy7f9iag52gwFYJbPCQ%2F0%3F" data-w="576" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;“大傻”成奎安的知名度要更高一些，缘于他的演出生涯参演过300多部电影，600多集电视剧。其中90%以上都是反派，而这些反派几乎一半以上都叫同一个名字：大傻。究竟是哪一部电影开始叫大傻的，已经无法去考证了。从《英雄本色》中，李子雄身旁无名的马仔，到《古惑仔》中吃鱼的一方大哥，每一个角色都是反派或是配角。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">凡是有黑帮大哥，打手，小弟，马仔的香港片，很难找到不是成奎安作为反派的电影。《喋血双雄》中扮演的汪海，被枪口伸到嘴中的场景，是很多人的记忆，这也使得四大恶人之中，“大傻”的名气最大。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5466666666666666" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYQ9tAOibzXsBsfsdV7k9BGbicjoxlBnC971xaBUC4dcC0odgb6GxtqEnQ%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">以上三个人最出名的一次反派表演，出现在1987年的电影《监狱风云》中，在这部周润发，梁家辉两位影帝参演的电影中，何家驹是一号反派人物，大咪，十足的可恨，同心狠手辣的典狱长勾结，残害无辜的狱友。监狱本就暗无天日，而大咪的出现，让监狱更加阴森恐怖。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何家驹此后的很多电影，反派角色都没有超越《监狱风云》中大咪的阴险，可见反派超越自己也并不容易。</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5714285714285714" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYOiazic0SfeQGSib60gIl4W3EcW6PyJrx9Ch2HrDGBIn3ns7Z8S6u9MB4Q%2F0%3F" data-w="784" title="p1210800721.jpg" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">《监狱风云》的另一个人物是由黄光亮饰演的傻标，傻标正如其名，更多的时候傻里傻气，是个没有头脑但又很讲义气的小头目。他逞强爱面子，却不失情调。当新年的钟声敲响，黄光亮和周润发、梁家辉在邓丽君《甜蜜蜜》的歌声里翩翩起舞。到了《监狱风云2》，这哥们还没出狱，依旧还是监狱中的带头大哥，狱友们打赌时输光所有香烟的一幕，实在让人忍俊不禁。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.5714285714285714" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkfuXcFG5VkGRAjFozXGuibWP9mhNkXkUKblkyHOTKXicK3Luk1wGxqdPEJ3mnd6GsDHD7D8AoFibPMg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif" data-type="gif" data-w="280" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">其实黄光亮的模样有一些喜剧感，一脸横肉并不意味着就是坏人。而“大傻”成奎安在《监狱风云》中尽管没几句台词，开场就在群架中被打倒了，但大傻一脸横肉的形象，实在是让人过目不忘。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.5625" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkfuXcFG5VkGRAjFozXGuibWLtfNMvwicSgdvjCtoICeic3b0chYNmy8lTzrnMY4ARg2FqgWY5mqRruQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif" data-type="gif" data-w="400" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.6936274509803921" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYTzJsNGbcrjibrr2Lp5oUWdiaA4vUM9ibLbLibKt34ef9RmHOxxTIbTICqQ%2F0%3F" data-w="408" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;相比于成奎安的横肉，李兆基尽管形象上与大傻并无太多差别，高大威猛的身形，很难与好人的形象联系起来。但与其他三个人不同的是，三个恶人都是靠演戏出名，而李兆基早年就是香港三合会成员，后金盆洗手进入了电影圈，所以在电影里当黑社会，纯粹是本色出演。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">更多的时候，基哥都是小配角，戏份不多，但没有他当反派，总觉得少了点什么。基哥的代表作品便是《喜剧之王》中收保护费的大哥，《古惑仔》系列也少不了基哥的身影。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5551663747810858" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYmWbSwxYhmk8IgcdyUR06fZaibwjWz3JR2Q1FM4p8CQunrjdxKPGzkdw%2F0%3F" data-w="571" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">近年来，在四大恶人或息影，或离世之时，低调的李兆基依旧活跃在影坛中，在《扫毒》、《夺命金》中客串角色，终于不演基哥了，反而让人无比怀念四大恶人时代的香港黑帮电影。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.7666666666666667" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vY1WJX0ofia1Hu7acxI5oH5Zpic1AJUFRriapIxibicZIqOalCKKfqkyVxH5Q%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">四大恶人虽然出演了很多反派，但可能还只是个小头目，不一定是个大反派。说起大反派，不能避开的人物便是张耀扬。模特出身的张耀扬出演过八十多部电影，当过那英MV的男主角。但最出名的还是他一脸邪气的表演，创造了无数经典反派角色。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从《只手遮天》的东星乌鸦、《战无不胜》的东星耀扬、到《监狱风云》的鬼见愁、《学校风云》的潇洒哥。无论是面对敌人，朋友，还是自己的老大，这个反派角色目中无人，绝不手软。 张耀扬是绝对的演技派，即便是出演好人，观众们都害怕他在片尾时，突然拔枪毙了其他人，这才是张耀扬的特点。 张耀扬最经典的反派角色依然是《监狱风云》中的鬼见愁，好吧，这个监狱集中了很多犯人，而这部电影汇集了太多的反派。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5769230769230769" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYWh7icOsVxu9kVU8snnDoVdARduhHu8SbXiaeX3C7iaXBjDleVKHH5nthQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="624" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本应当正义的典狱长，在本片中也是无比邪恶。张耀扬的演技简直狂拽炫酷耪ㄌ欤霸气十足，行事凶狠，不计后果。尽管至今并没有任何奖项对张耀扬的演技做出肯定，但在那个录像厅时代，叛逆的少年们除了记住古惑仔陈浩南，山鸡，也记住了那个邪恶的东星乌鸦。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">张耀扬是影迷心中当之无愧的无冕之王。反派四大天王的称号，也是对一生只演反派的张耀扬，最好的勉励。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYfiaWo9D6GAHoiak9nsVd5pENFzUMHouDz95J9wWA88JVck29G55xN0GA%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">说起演技，不得不提到，刘洵。这个名字可能对你有点陌生，但是他饰演过的人物你一定记得：《倩女幽魂2》中的蜈蚣精，《笑傲江湖》中的东厂头目，《新龙门客栈》里的东厂三巨头之首贾公公，还有那个在《九品芝麻官》中与周星驰对骂，却被狂喷的李公公。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5236363636363637" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYQolgmFc51XHbcCbAKiaS9mhoiaOJUsxibH6JJ52WGx2kicW9jDdqeX1ZIQ%2F0%3F" data-w="550" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为香江梨园行里享有盛誉的京剧和粤剧名家，自然一身仙风道骨的作风，颇有贵族气质，早年在电影《刀马旦》中担任戏曲指导，后逐渐进入影坛，即使是饰演反派也是高级反派，如太监头目，武林高手，一代宗师。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.625" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYltsRavwsebQPicEX4ASg6kxrwuJdeO9qelwtNkL83tFEAPrbSOWBDIw%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;刘老先生的代表作品便是武侠片《新龙门客栈》的贾公公一角，演技绝不输梁家辉，张曼玉等一干大腕明星，反派的效果要远超出甄子丹最后出演的大BOSS。刘洵的台词功力，眼神表情的神韵到位，十足地衬托出贾廷这个反派的奸诈，打戏一招一式，有板有眼，台风纯正，可见其扎实的戏曲功底。 2013年，王家卫邀请74岁的刘老先生出演《一代宗师》中的角色瑞先生，便是对这位香港武侠电影著名的反派，最好的致敬。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.6716666666666666" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYBgpQ2dvCt2m8u9vx0QabXB3xYTsfOqMiaBqILKMJh06EnXGLasCUvNw%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">武侠片的反派，不仅长相邪恶，还需要一定的功夫基础，没有武艺高强的反派，怎么能凸显出咱们少林弟子李连杰的强大呢？这就不得不提到计春华。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为浙江省武术队的退役队员，因1982年的电影《少林寺》中的秃鹰一角而名声大震，进入影坛，进而被香港导演看中，参演了很多香港电影的反派角色，如《新少林五祖》和《方世玉》。但计春华老师非常谦虚，曾经承认自己演技不足，拍电影也是为了心中的武术梦想。演反派，别人靠演技和模样，计老师靠的是真本事。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.4816666666666667" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYHEGZibNuMBbSN7AQ9iciaqErxSDzoOdtSd6fwHMX1qj0QQSHYv1UUmtgA%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">计春华的代表作品自然是那部让他成名的《少林寺》，在这部电影中，无论是主角还是配角，正义的少林弟子，还是大反派，每一个形象都令人印象深刻。而计老师凭借的天生穷凶极恶的面相和一身如假包换的真功夫，成为那个时代功夫电影，当之无愧的反派BOSS。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.54" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYadz7kRyv6YaZADeva6vPTmwHCW8CHyicu37FicxJHr8hWp8lAh97DDHQ%2F0%3F" data-w="500" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">出演反派角色，很多时候全因自己那一张邪气的脸，邹兆龙则并非如此。他有着完美的身材和硬朗的身手，可在电影也是反派角色，或许最初是与李连杰合作出演反派的关系，所以一直被定位在反派形象上。在《中南海保镖》以及《赤子威龙》中，都要和李连杰过招。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYiaVRXjG52XodPG7pmXUmqlbbhTKUjMvcFrOtibrQLm53s0R47UBRZoSw%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为香港功夫片大哥洪金宝的徒弟，邹兆龙从替身演员做起，台词少不要紧，打戏多才是关键。当然，邹兆龙在众多反派角色中，是运气最好的。 2001年在好莱坞大片《黑客帝国2：重装上阵》中，出演先知的保镖，与主角尼奥的对手戏，留给观众非常深刻的印象。而且最关键的是这一角色不是反派了，这可是很多功夫演员一生的梦想：走进好莱坞，出演一个角色，而不是当一个花瓶或站桩。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">比如甄子丹，在《刀锋战士》中连一句台词都没有，而邹兆龙在《黑客帝国》中有充足的打戏，有足够的台词，实在是幸运的很，可见，反派演员到了一定程度，也会有属于自己的春天 。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYICJAxIlubOFmVM1ZXdfBS4N8tN1k0BNh57jbDJk0BamWNpC74TufDQ%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
    <p></p>
    <section class="" data-id="85446" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
     <section style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">反派四大天王</span></span>
     </section>
     <section style="margin: 2px 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px rgb(33, 33, 34); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <section data-width="40%" style="padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 2px; padding-left: 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 258.391px; border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
      <section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">之前</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">提到香港电影反派四大天王之一的张耀扬，那么现在再来说说其余三位，个个都是影坛大哥级人物。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.73" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYOHfjNCY12Epy3lfUJpzsXTzQFWnO8pZjkWBhR3y7zaGQibakaIpCEaQ%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">首先绝对的大哥大，任达华。作为香港影坛的绝对实力派，很难用语言描述华仔的演技，无论是正义主角，还是邪恶的反派，各种各样的角色，任达华几乎都尝试过，没有任何一个演员像任达华这样，有这么全面的戏路。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5568965517241379" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYoiceSDX4xSo2jXEGBJpYFtxxicraXkeSBoyZqOb0MYYoKgNYs9Ev2viaQ%2F0%3F" data-w="580" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他的形象亦正亦邪，从三级片起家，在众多烂片中磨练出来深厚的演技，反派人物也是他早年最擅长的角色。单看反派角色，从《古惑仔》里的洪兴蒋先生，《龙城岁月》里的阿乐，到《侠盗高飞》里的判官，每一个角色都是可以写进电影学院表演系教科书中。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他出演的反派性格复杂，或张狂，或内敛，既可以演警察，又可以演变态。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.7466666666666667" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYzA55ibmXvJSxk0NHg6urgPL1lV4ia3v3lpfYlDPv3pAuspLsygez0hSg%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">同样与任达华有着相似经历的香港大反派，就是黄秋生。同样作为香港影坛的影帝级人物，黄秋生是靠烂片起家。中英混血的黄sir本来很帅气，可惜迫于生计，接了大量的烂片，而使得他的角色定位成了配角或反派角色。演过的角色更是包罗万象，丰富多彩。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.42" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYqNqcAZdEjgpu9icB54dTQOTAvDv5wibhic3IJPlSQymf52Mm57lxZCmwg%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从警察到杀人犯，从黑帮老大到变态杀手，一切人物都被他那亦正亦邪的面孔演绎的淋漓尽致。《枪火》里沉默稳重的阿鬼，《辣手神探》中的黑帮老大，《冲锋队之怒火街头》中的悍匪。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">黄秋生的表演很少有大开大合，过度卖力的时候，一切都看似自然。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5416666666666666" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYWtHCM8R6y4zVXhng2qLnTqFK02MszoU3MdggrqZJCiaXVxYdGGAsYVg%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5183333333333333" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYUjicxBESNofzTsftaynv1K6soCnrAuzfwiaWEVqF9v1xTlsOQmflyuuw%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">最出名的是《无间道》里的黄sir，不过那是正面角色，暂时不表，说一说黄sir最让人印象深刻的反派角色， 那就是《古惑仔》系列中一身朋克风的大飞，这个电影系列并非足够优秀，却是很多80后的童年记忆。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.55" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vY9wcibEDSHaRnphdjIiaL9sZJicg6WPn7ssBlO7O0OsU2TrUIFnG1HhGwA%2F0%3F" data-w="580" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYjAO938hzVwCbWgFd1PeuSoEbFpL2GicaHMGxugxDgBnEZkIRmcTHIjA%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">恶人四大天王的最后一位，吴镇宇，也是一个反派专业户。如果反派可以分等级的话，吴镇宇绝对是一个高级反派。作为TVB电视剧默默无闻近十年的小龙套，吴镇宇成名于1996年的《古惑仔之人在江湖》，靓坤一角。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5531453362255966" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYwbaiazicr52fWS1PQY7icBicAYOnq95vjwujHVd8XeENKTEfXkhib5iaYFTg%2F0%3F" data-w="461" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这是一个极具个性的黑帮大佬形象，眼神犀利，面部狰狞，心狠手辣，这个反派角色实在是深入人心，使得他自己也难于突破， 直到2003年《无间道2》再次出演反派。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vY9LmzRfVht7IBicFGxVWtRsZ30waBEhr2HtNiaicUysBvppUYkFDSUMHqQ%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这部电影的反派太多，比如老道的韩琛，比如杀人之后吹口琴的三叔，廖启智，再比如在电影宣传海报中，被远远放在了后面的，是吴镇宇饰演的倪永孝，在整部电影中，这个反派形象远远超过了此片实际主角陈冠希和余文乐。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.485" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkfuXcFG5VkGRAjFozXGuibWyzEPlI7FjXX25RnTPYhwdQaco6zmza7yua0YVBkqquKdOTyWq3sSZA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif" data-type="gif" data-w="400" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不同于以往的反派，倪永孝掌握着整个黑帮家族的兴衰，他沉稳冷静，温文尔雅，杀人富有计划性和传统文化感，是标准的衣冠禽兽。从倪永孝开始掌管家族事务伊始，就使得本片就有了一种经典黑帮片《教父》的即视感。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.4844961240310077" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkfuXcFG5VkGRAjFozXGuibWFdbCnkcT5lgwIIYnClpY1SQLdzian2ibWia0d0rhErbKn4hfMricZJCrSg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif" data-type="gif" data-w="516" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">正如《教父》所倡导的家族至上，倪永孝对家庭有着极强的责任感，对于家人的极度信任和保护，这与其对黑帮严格的管理和多疑排外，形成了鲜明的对比。他对触犯家族利益的人心狠手辣、不留情面，家庭是他的生命，可惜这也是被韩琛牢牢抓住的弱点。在生命的最后一刻，倪永孝终于解脱了，他努力让自己同父异母的弟弟陈永仁重回大家庭，也选择把窃听器塞回他的口袋里，倒在警察弟弟的怀里，也许是他一生宿命的最大讽刺。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="z-index: -1; cursor: pointer; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.45267489711934156" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYGfQroHwoWL1CqYQpLOtQ7ibenB54bVZhF50R1rf3Td2JM2tKtUibCPFQ%2F0%3F" data-w="486" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">可惜的是吴镇宇这位“中国教父”，</span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这样爆发式演技，恐怕很难重来，也是华语电影中最巅峰的反派演绎。这也是吴镇宇独立于其他反派演员之处，其他演员都可以重复戏路，但吴镇宇此生也许再也无法超越自己，超越倪永孝了。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
    <p></p>
    <section class="" data-id="86275" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
     <section class="" style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
      <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 30px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">ABOUT</span></p>
      <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
       <section style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0.8em; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-top-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); height: 10px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-left-width: 0.8em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 0.8em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;"></section>
       <section style="padding-bottom: 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);">
        <section style="padding: 0.5em 1.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96) rgb(239, 112, 96) rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">
         <p class="" data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">香港电影的黄金时代</p>
        </section>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
     <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
    </section>
    <p></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkCU93b3KqqRr6OJ89NR8vYjJjsWBWRNtaysacJuic9icjcicBX1rHlqucgugRdGjXpRPWHgTqJARoiaQ%2F0%3F" data-w="600" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">香港电影发展至今，已有百年，有着无数有趣的题材和角色，这其中既有拉风帅气的小马哥，也有亦正亦邪的铜锣湾陈浩南。</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.555" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2F0w2XDoeR5VkfuXcFG5VkGRAjFozXGuibWicjG8fV64vk46SpibhfSo6gEHJ8roQt2FcoXEsDviblLHvMADXbX0ppQQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif" data-type="gif" data-w="400" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这一切的一切，都曾是我们童年时代的美好回忆。作为曾经亚洲电影的巅峰，如今已经急流勇退，我们很难再看到当年的经典，而那些经典的反派角色，也成为了我们一去不复返，又无法替代的银幕记忆。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 31px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; height: auto !important;"><img style="font-family: Calibri; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 474px !important;" width="474px" data-w="843" data-ratio="0.07829181494661921" src="img.jsp?id=593584&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2FsvgxOMD0rYNXSaHoMvIC7EsD4YQYqicSPgLFYrDicIjN7yz4ZUeGicQkZGMlSDxibLNO4abS9ewhibBEdNian1WzYHFw%2F0" /></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal;"><br /></p>
